ead to CMB bispectrum constraints on modified initial states already\ncompeting with those derived from the power spectrum.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 26 Jan 2009 16:57:25 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 11 May 2009 11:53:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2010-01-05"}
