ics imaging, with a resolution of 0.2\" provides a\nreference frame for subsequent studies of future periods of activity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 26 Jan 2009 21:00:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-13"}
